{"tid":2254800,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 免焗 純手搓 南瓜平底鍋麵包","createTime":"2020-10-23T05:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T12:29:17.000Z","uid":30742,"like":47,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e7eb36897a5aef1999c59576d07aa98335d2be09","tid":2254800,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cC-IZlTTJDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcC-IZlTTJDw&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=777948e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cC-IZlTTJDw</a>     <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHLcBx2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHLcBx2.gif&h=4601cd7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qq17qrq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQq17qrq.gif&h=c8f30a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企兩老近排南瓜收成，要諗諗計清晒佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bFHequ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bFHequ.jpg&h=b9e20dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次佢地見我做bagel<br />\n就話想試下整麵包 <br />\n但屋企無焗爐 <br />\n所以今日我要整一個純手搓，免焗既麵包！<br />\n用煎pan煎既麵包 <br />\n加上佢地一定無耐性慢慢搓<br />\n所以5分鐘就要極速搓好！<br />\n當晚即時比某人品評過，鬆軟、好食， <br />\n而家南瓜勁平，大家都可以試下！<br />\n<br />\n圖文blog <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/10/pumpkin-bread-in-fry-pan-eggless.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F10%2Fpumpkin-bread-in-fry-pan-eggless.html&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=49822b86\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/10/pumpkin-bread-in-fry-pan-eggless.html</a> <br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=df834008\" target=\"